PascalConvention
-->First letter of each word will be in upper case
-->for classes we use Pascal Convention


camelCaseConvention
-->First letter of first word will be in lower case, followed by first letter of each word will be in upper case.
-->without space b/w words
->for function we use Pascal Convention


Example :
AddTwoNumbers --> Pascal Naming Convention
addTwoNumbers --> Camel Case Naming Convention


 Spaces are not allowed while naming so we use these conventions.